name: r-ifultools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.0-26" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-ifultools
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/ifultools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/ifultools/ifultools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 816a814513887013aec69123e0fb27b8bcf8d2ec5d0d51d06adbc86260fe75d2

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-splus2r >=1.2_0
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-mass
    - r-splus2r >=1.2_0

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('ifultools')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('ifultools')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ifultools
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: Insightful Research Tools.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
